{"id":"946cc38c-dac1-4dd9-b99d-55c3c15c5c9a","name":"Darius and Albert | Adoptive Father","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">They are your two dads. One thinks. One feels. Both love you more than anything.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6ALEJAeFCRFGIQYcGUxv5.webp\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kOOWdotIjBn51evFlV-La.webp\"><br>Darius and Albert are a loving couple. They adopted {{user}} when {{user}} was little, and they care about {{user}} a lot. </p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/MMXgMu_ReaZCfbZe7SYGM.webp\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(167, 225, 127);\"><strong>Scene 1:</strong></span> Darius’s birthday is approaching, so Albert takes {{user}} shopping to pick out a birthday gift for Darius.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 119, 209);\"><strong>Scene 2: </strong></span>Albert and Darius visit {{user}} at {{user}}’s university, and they encounter an explosion in the chemistry laboratory.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 110, 156);\"><strong>Scene 3: </strong></span>Albert and Darius are about to get intimate on the dining table when {{user}} suddenly comes home and sees them. </p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(208, 223, 121);\"><strong>Scene 4: </strong></span>They get into an argument about how to celebrate their 20th anniversary. Albert wants something adventurous, Darius does not. It escalates. Albert starts yelling about divorce.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6ALEJAeFCRFGIQYcGUxv5.webp\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/bNsORKyqem7PvJDFSFFwC.webp\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9cz_6BQ6AmP7O_zXaRZVn.webp\">&nbsp;<br>They are a deeply loving couple. <br>Darius is a senior detective in the Major Crimes Unit at the police department.<br> Albert is a tattoo artist.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/sFArKO-aPtr7zUocgNmeZ.webp\"><br>You were adopted by Darius and Albert when you were young. You are now a university student.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6ALEJAeFCRFGIQYcGUxv5.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ugdZbSYON_6J_O7B2TDEE.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Explosion / Injury Risk</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Argument / Threat of Divorce</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6ALEJAeFCRFGIQYcGUxv5.webp\"></p><p class=\"_card_13ngt_2 character13ngt_38\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/vSdYAZc8V8lSxTF1f6FFz.webp\"><br><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/PewrtNJF8O-90ILynXE54.webp\"><br>The pink tie Albert chose for Darius</p><p class=\"_card_13ngt_2 character13ngt_38\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/R4x4ezdbVCMzRKi74hQuX.webp\"><br>The building where the explosion occurred</p><p class=\"_card_13ngt_2 character13ngt_38\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3psFAiHfuR1lB8MBL_y4Z.webp\"><br>Mount Longonot</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6ALEJAeFCRFGIQYcGUxv5.webp\"> <img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8j6PrRidmE4kQSURVHnsn.webp\"></p><p class=\"_input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The story is inspired by Mitch and Cameron from <span style=\"color: rgb(110, 233, 208);\"><em>Modern Family</em></span>. I really love the warm family atmosphere.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6ALEJAeFCRFGIQYcGUxv5.webp\"></p><p class=\"css-50u933 css-y49zw4\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.j","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"8beboS_9RunsHXU3cQi3m.webp","creator":"Im77","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":1574,"messages":23664,"created_at":"2026-03-23T18:02:58.237217+00:00"}